hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: A law firm yourpharmstore.com Often, in print at least, a man is described as a gentlemen because of the way he looks - his suit and his demeanour. I have been in the fashion industry now for 13 years and I've had the privilege of meeting some of the most powerful men, not just in fashion, but in business, film, music and so on. You come to learn that not all powerful and well-dressed men can be defined as gentlemen - far from it in some cases.
